Today for #ARTISTSFORBLACKLIVES I‚Äôm spotlighting Black Church Food Security. 
A little bit about this great organization in their words - 
We work with congregations to establish gardens and agricultural projects on Black Church-owned land.

We link farmers with congregations for niche farmer‚Äôs markets which happen inside places of worship.

We conduct asset-mapping of Black Churches and the neighborhoods where they are located to help leverage their resources and build power for historically marginalized Black communities.

Today for #ARTISTSFORBLACKLIVES I‚Äôm spotlighting @thelovelandfoundation. 
Loveland Foundation is committed to showing up for communities of color in unique and powerful ways, with a particular focus on Black women and girls. Check the link in my stories to learn more and contribute what you can! üíó

Woke Vote empowers individuals to fight back against policies that are antithetical to our shared values. By meeting people where they are and teaching the fundamentals of congregation and community organizing, we are altering the political landscape as we know it. We know that these hidden faces and voices ‚Äî our faces and voices ‚Äîhave the power to reshape our democracy, influence and lead movements, and invoke lasting change. Their mission: To invest in the activation, long-term engagement, training and development of new organizers, and mobilization of historically disengaged voters of color. 
Join the movement today! #WokeVote @wokevote #ARTISTSFORBLACKLIVES

From the outside, music may seem like a new thing for me, but I always knew growing up that I wanted to do both music and acting.  I wasn't sure how or when I could make that happen, but it was something I always knew I wanted to achieve.

Being recognized as a "crossover artist" is that moment of validation and personal realization for me that I am accomplishing what I set out to achieve a long time ago. I'm so grateful to my fans for supporting me throughout my career and for allowing me to express myself as an artist in both mediums.
